dct_title_s: New Jersey- New York: Staten Island Quadrangle
dct_description_sm: United States. Geological Survey. U.S.G.S. Alternate title: Staten Island, N.J.-N.Y. Relief shown by 20 feet contour intervals. Triangulation by U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey. Topography by U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey. Surveyed in 1888-89 and 1897. Verso: legend and explanatory notes, "The topographic maps of the United States".
